items.title: Mainframe sort merge - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Mainframe sort merge - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
The Sort/Merge utility is a mainframe program to sort records in a file into a 
specified order, merge pre-sorted files into a sorted file, or copy selected records.
